                <h1>Understanding Dobbs v. Jackson: A Landmark Abortion Case</h1>
                <p>Dobbs v. Jackson Women's Health Organization is a landmark Supreme Court case that challenges the constitutionality of Mississippi's 15-week abortion ban. Decided in June 2022, the ruling overturned Roe v. Wade, giving states more power to regulate abortions. The case highlights ongoing debates over reproductive rights and personal freedoms.</p>
